To answer your questions.<br>
<br>
Color series will not break mezz and it does work on mobs up to around level 55.<br>
<br>
However, doing it in a crowd is a great way of dying so be careful its a lot of aggro.  As you level up, you will find that mobs continue to hit much harder.  In your 40s, they start doubling for around 100 or so.  By now in the PoV, they double for 800 or so.  The last thing you want in PoV is aggro, unless its slowed.<br>
<br>
So, my advice is that you really start looking at how things change over time.  Advice that is good at 20 fails by the time you are 50 and that fails at the time you are 60.<br>
<br>
The only time I even load up the color series anymore is for AE groups.  Below 50, I always had 2 color series spells loaded.<br>
<br>
Cames Houdini<br>
