<br>
Color shift and color skew will give you time to get a mez off.  Color flux will only let you get a mez off if you use an insta-clicky to reset recast time.  Color skew will let you get a slow off only if you use an insta-clicky.  Worst comes to worst, color skew will let you get a gate off, color shift only if you insta-click.<br>
<br>
However, tier2+ mobs are immune to stun, so I can only keep word of morrell memmed, which is a 6 second PB mez instead of a stun.  It does the job though- WoM will let you get CoD off w/ help from an insta-clicky.  Be warned though, it seems to be somewhat random duration, sometimes it lasts longer than normal, sometimes it lasts shorter.  Without an insta-click, I can get CoD off maybe 30% of the time. <p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><br>
